          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:02.028Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Thank you, Mr. Smith. My name is Sarah Mitchell from First National Bank. This is an attempt to collect a debt. Before we proceed, may I have your consent to record this call?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:05.226Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Okay, I understand.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:08.304Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Just to clarify, do you consent to having this call recorded for documentation purposes?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:10.296Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Yes, I consent to the recording.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:13.989Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Thank you. Now, Mr. Smith, the outstanding balance is $2,450, and it's 45 days past due. We can discuss payment options. Are you able to make a full payment today, or would you like to explore a payment plan?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:18.176Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "I’d like to explore a payment plan, please.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:22.248Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "I understand, Mr. Smith. We can definitely explore a payment plan. We have options to break the total into installments. Can you tell me what monthly amount might be manageable for you?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:25.670Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "I think around $200 a month would be manageable for me.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:29.518Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Thank you for that information, Mr. Smith. At $200 a month, it would take about 12 months to clear the balance, including any interest. Would you be comfortable committing to that, or do you need a different arrangement?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:34.271Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "I’m comfortable with that arrangement, yes.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:38.341Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Great. We'll set up a payment plan at $200 a month. When would you like to make your first payment—would the end of this week work for you?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:41.364Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Yes, the end of this week works for me.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:45.169Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Understood. Let's schedule your first payment for the end of this week. Would Friday or Saturday work better for you?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:47.915Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Friday would be better for me.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:51.889Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "All right, we’ll set the first payment for this Friday. Now, let’s confirm your preferred payment method—would you like to use a bank account or a debit card for these monthly payments?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:55.102Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "I’d prefer to use my bank account for the payments.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:37:59.992Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Thank you for letting me know. We can set up the payments directly from your bank account. I'll need the account and routing numbers to finalize the arrangement. When you’re ready, you can provide those details.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:04.697Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "All right, let me grab that information real quick. I'll read it out to you in a moment.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:09.963Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Take your time, Mr. Smith. Once you have the account and routing numbers, we’ll get everything set up smoothly for your payment plan.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:13.013Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Thank you for your patience. I've got the details now. Here we go.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:16.809Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "You're welcome. Go ahead and share the routing number first, and then the account number when you're ready.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:19.799Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "All right, the routing number is 021-000021, and the account number is 4567-891234.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:25.625Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Thank you, Mr. Smith. I’ve noted the routing number as 021000021 and the account number as 4567891234. Your first payment of $200 will be set for this Friday. I’ll generate a confirmation and provide you with a reference number shortly.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:32.389Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Sounds good. I'll wait for that confirmation and the reference number.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:37.641Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Thank you for your patience. Here’s your confirmation: your payment plan is set at $200 a month, starting this Friday. Your reference number is FNB-4721-JS. You’re all set, Mr. Smith. Thank you for working with me today.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:42.361Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "I appreciate your help as well. Thank you, and I’ll make sure everything stays on track.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:47.333Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "You're very welcome, Mr. Smith. We appreciate that commitment. If you have any questions or need assistance along the way, don’t hesitate to reach out. Have a great day.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:50.551Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Thank you, I will. You have a great day too.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:54.683Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "Thank you, Mr. Smith. Just to confirm, is there anything else you’d like to go over or any details you need clarified before we wrap up?",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:38:57.619Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "No, I’m all set. Thanks again for your assistance. I’m good to wrap up now.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-01T20:39:02.446Z"
